revision.text:
{{refimprove|date=December 2014}}

Anti-submarine drones are [[Unmanned surface vehicle]]s designed to stalk and hunt submarines.<ref>http://www.foxnews.com/tech/2014/07/17/construction-starts-on-anti-submarine-drone/</ref> They are an emerging technology with a prototype [[ACTUV]] being designed by [[DARPA]] as a potentially smaller, more efficient [[Anti-submarine warfare]] capability for the [[United States Navy]]. 

